Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}似てても違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}マンダリン　オレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}友達　恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}２人のココロも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私は逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そしたら光も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:41.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}射してはくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡なのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}出逢いも恋も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}種もつぼみも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:58.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ青い　実でさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色は　あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見た夕焼けを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出させてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}２つの影が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}手を繋いでるみたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:15.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}甘くなるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:20.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}それともしぼんじゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私の未来知りたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:38.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだけど泣けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:44.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色に　早く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:46.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なりたい果実
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}キミの光を浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想や夢は膨らむばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:56.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}気づいてよ　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:58.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}食べてみたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだすっぱくて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:06.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私みたいで残せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:22.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}泣けるよ　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:24.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだよ
