Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然相似却并不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mandarin  orange
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朋友  恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}2颗悸动的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为不想伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}于是就连阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:41.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也再也无法照进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明明就是奇迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}邂逅也是恋爱也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}种子也是花蕾也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:58.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就连仍然青涩的果实也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:06.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}橙色  让我想起了那天的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}两个人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就好像牵着手一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:15.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}橙子  何时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}才能变得甘甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:20.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还是会枯萎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要知道我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}才全部全部吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好酸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:38.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然喜欢你  却会哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:46.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:56.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:59.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸涩  不禁落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:06.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不能让它像我一样被丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}全部吃完了  喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好酸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:22.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要哭了哦  喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:24.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢你哦
