Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学从左边  我从右边  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长  他们在走廊跑起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就宽大处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上了要说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在入口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河  听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂大河  你一直都想知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也喜欢高须同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢高须龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢着  一直喜欢着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一直觉得必须把他让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好朋友的你需要高须同学什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是傲慢的我的误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也小看了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也说过吧  我的幸福由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的  你的幸福也只有你才能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以大河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看你的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚才摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,止住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳  还以为要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都会这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这也是一种回报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗  我说过我有能看得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢  那是自己的…意气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意气？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过我打棒球的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我也打过棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了  还是我比较有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却没能坚持下去  因为是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  打算存了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力考上体育大学  以全国级垒球为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊  对着全世界呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我所选择并获得的幸福就是它了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的意气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为执着于这个  我决定不再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算难过痛苦  也决定要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果有谁能看着我难过痛苦和哭泣也是回报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个发夹怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个一定是要在平安夜送我作礼物的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  一开始真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为是大河送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明决定不接受了  明明因此伤害了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在高须同学面前戴着它  我想为此道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…现在在什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我房间里  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我不能收下那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  还有一个能看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学喜欢大河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  高须同学  我们就此再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着看得到的东西冲刺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊  高须
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须Hey  高须～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人还算正直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就算逃了也一定会来打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…关于刚才的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了小实的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工结束了再听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…如果我再想逃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说谎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰…泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹别扭也该有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人又能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是高须同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你一直照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子今后要和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要和你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的男人  还有他的小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白的是泰泰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定好禁止打工的  但是小龙你却说谎破坏了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不能原谅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了我增加工作  所以才倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以由我来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是家人  家人这样互相扶持是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人的事我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要我家的小龙努力学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到自己想做的事  出色地活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有学习的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做自己想做的事  没成为出色的人的不都是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把自己的失败推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事业失败就逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  然后就叫我的亲生母亲来养我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那个人已经有新的家庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子里有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人个子很高  所以出生的孩子的腿一定也会很长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我像是个未进化的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的…这样的家庭我怎么融入得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在的话  家里就变得不自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋老爸那里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有我在大家才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…一直…这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰子一定会有更好的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是高中也还能重新读
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人都很任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会根据自己的情况来连累他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  也许正是我在连累泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…还是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  如果没有我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  你这猪脑袋  不要轻生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像有个很大的误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秃子秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做又能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「都是因为我在」这种天真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也说了啊  刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你喜欢谁  不管你今后会和谁一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想看着你…看着你高须龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以不要再说自己不在就好了这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事个头啊  你想杀了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊  我不是说过道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是会斤斤计较啊  啥血型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是金牛座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座占卜啥的我不太懂  成吉思汗很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}成吉思汗：这里指的是日本的一种羊肉料理，发源于北海道，\N在一种铁制的形状如帽子的特制锅上，将羊肉片和蔬菜蘸上调料汁，边烤边吃。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2个月后我就18岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样从泰子她们那里逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃啊逃啊  睡了醒了  再逃啊逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我的生日  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就嫁给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我们也是大人了  不会让任何人妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死之前我的人生都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我…等等——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾  不是说好我先说给你听的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只狡猾狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  这种事就该让男人说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我说  我和小实说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让她看看我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么…一起说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了  在这种重要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无…无视掉  快点继续  又冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊  那不是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂高须  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和逢坂的家人为了找你们到处联络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  现在就到我说的地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等  北村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发上粘到了鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在你家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的母亲的包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没来过我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天阿姨她们也不在  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会感冒的  先去淋浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直走到底右转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这些也拿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让你来费心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河  鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  高须同学的换洗衣服佑作会拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  喜欢大河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢大河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一脸傻样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你逼我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙你这家伙你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实小实  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河  大河…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多事麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  比起这个今后你们打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算私奔GEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是认真的GEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  还剩两个月…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认同个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私奔然后结婚？  这也太飞越了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等龙儿18岁嘛  这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了你们打算睡在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之商务旅馆或漫画咖啡厅之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一直都持续那样的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  所以回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还回得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出搜索的请求  传闻传到学校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好会退学的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望的东西总是会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以决定什么都不再抱希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的心意得到了回报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想要打破这个「希望的东西总是会坏掉」的厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  必须打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我贴身放了很久的存折
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工积攒的钱都存在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点  完全都不觉得你们是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对无法赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果这就是你的做法的话我也不能反对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了终有一天把它还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  我家别墅的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去过一次的话应该知道在哪儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我忘了怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}米券
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么亚美  今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实我和亚美还有些悄悄话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们和好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢  笨蛋吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快走吧  这家伙也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  小实  笨蛋吉  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定还会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰软了已经站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  要给我看你的哭脸么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪可是心灵的鼻血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为了什么而流的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为大河被高须同学抢走了？  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再哭泣…明明已经决定了绝对不再哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难为情的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  也明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊上跌倒会流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生中跌倒会流眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋吗  我们要谈人生还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后  十年后  二十年后  六十年后都会继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了一定要逃出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰泰的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…对了  把干燥机带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想只有我的行李很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么别拿些轻飘飘的衣服来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会增加体积
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完了马上出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事的话马上打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  立刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹦…小鹦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外公和外婆的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们看了这个手表就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}一直以来谢谢你的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  魅罗乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚时来联络说是暂时要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有多小孩子气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算过了生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是不会长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天不是刚炫耀过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吃掉吧  打算让人看到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到保质期快过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说学校不是交换巧克力的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有交换啊  我只是拿来而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧大河…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请假了  高须同学也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  两个人一起感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油加油加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大桥加油加油加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不去送行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算内心再坚强的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大河和高须同学一起甩了也不行了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要和你打雪仗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  纯洁的白球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是私奔用的食物  就选了些比较大人味的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  雪茄巧克力和鸡味仙贝  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也做了便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私奔的便当不应该是车站的便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人会在意也只是因为面子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会惹出大骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  泰泰怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是现在我能说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰泰说我们三个人是家人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里真是高兴得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家庭又是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想这样成为真的家人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰泰  会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是永别  所以说不是讨厌私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也觉得那样非常不错  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…大河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他爸…他他他他他他他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个的确是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是你们的外孙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须龙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这家伙是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是逃避  我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿让我看到的  只属于龙儿的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑哦  不要生气哦
